-Nami4dTLiMr5iCw2UNz.description: This deck is perfect for practicing the doubling rule when adding on a vowel suffix or consonant-le.

-Nami9-twBSGvYqDI1HW.description: Whether you call these welded sounds, glued sounds, wild old words, or closed syllable exceptions, this deck is great for practicing those trickier word families.

-NarqpewAp2p8H6inYXL.author: Summer Kiesel
